#🎮 How to Play

- Use arrow keys (↑ ↓ ← →) to control the pencil  
- The pencil continuously draws a path as it moves  
- Plan your movement carefully to avoid trapping yourself  
- A monster eraser constantly chases you and erases your trail  
- Avoid colliding with obstacles placed on the map  
- Do not cross your own drawn path  
- Stay alert and react quickly to escape tight situations  
- Survive as long as possible to achieve a higher score  
